  "3303700": {
    "name": "Vagnerun",
    "steam_appid": 3303700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/49ac84976de92c3d02bd13a6251d64ff.poster.avif?t=1733352570\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/49ac84976de92c3d02bd13a6251d64ff.webm?t=1733352570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/49ac84976de92c3d02bd13a6251d64ff.mp4?t=1733352570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Vagnerun</strong> 是一款自上而下的等距视角赛车游戏，融合了肾上腺素、策略和战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/4df95807458826e205278b37d69b20ff.poster.avif?t=1733352570\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/4df95807458826e205278b37d69b20ff.webm?t=1733352570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/4df95807458826e205278b37d69b20ff.mp4?t=1733352570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的星球上冒险，每个星球有3条充满挑战的赛道，布满独特的障碍和奖励。赢得比赛，积累积分，解锁新赛道，随着进度的推进，竞争会变得更加激烈。只有最有技巧和策略的车手才能生存并晋级到下一个阶段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/603e2698f382e10bc3592f25c8ba519e.avif?t=1733352570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras_big/603e2698f382e10bc3592f25c8ba519e.avif?t=1733352570 width=800 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在比赛之间，你可以利用一个强大的升级系统来改进你的飞船：升级发动机以获得更高的最高速度，增加氮气的容量和动力，强化装甲以抵抗更多伤害，并从五种射击类型中选择，以使你的对手保持防御状态。修理你的飞船，购买像护盾和轨道球这样的物品，准备不惜一切代价赢得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加最多10艘飞船的激烈比赛，在比赛中你可以跳跃并射击对手以争夺领先地位。支持双人分屏游戏模式，<strong>Vagnerun</strong> 承诺带来激烈的对决和难忘的本地乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/11a1ce304477519f205a7ba592fb5f5d.avif?t=1733352570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras_big/11a1ce304477519f205a7ba592fb5f5d.avif?t=1733352570 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过摧毁障碍物、消灭对手或在赛道上收集奖励来赚取金钱。面对竞争，在每组3条赛道中争取前三名的排名，以解锁下一个星球并继续你的银河之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/67adfee5acb0512026d47efd5480d638.avif?t=1733352570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras_big/67adfee5acb0512026d47efd5480d638.avif?t=1733352570 width=800 height=438 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >证明你是宇宙中最优秀的车手，完成征服所有星球的终极挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/8b69fbd5ed0d41da64a34cf648ab62a1.avif?t=1733352570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras_big/8b69fbd5ed0d41da64a34cf648ab62a1.avif?t=1733352570 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接 <strong>Vagnerun</strong> 带来的速度、策略和动作体验——在这里，胜利不仅仅是技巧的问题，更是生存之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras/98db0c275d102ff4a27af529eab562cb.avif?t=1733352570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303700/extras_big/98db0c275d102ff4a27af529eab562cb.avif?t=1733352570 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏主要特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>星际探索</strong>：在<strong>24个独特星球</strong>上竞速，每个星球都有<strong>3条具有挑战性的赛道</strong>，充满障碍、危险和等待发现的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>激烈的游戏模式</strong>：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锦标赛模式</strong>：在传统比赛中展现你的技能。每个星球的比赛中进入前三名，即可解锁下一个星球。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>淘汰赛模式</strong>：挑战逆向赛道并生存下来！每场比赛淘汰<strong>3名选手</strong>。在3条赛道结束后，<strong>仅有一名车手</strong>晋级到下一个星球。你能坚持到最后吗？</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级系统</strong>：定制你的飞船，成为银河中最具竞争力的赛车手！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提升性能</strong>，如升级引擎、加速器和氮气推进器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强化战斗策略</strong>，如装备护甲、武器和特殊道具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明智地选择升级方向，打造兼具速度、力量和策略的飞船。</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满动作的竞速</strong>：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与<strong>敌人交战</strong>，同时躲避陷阱和障碍物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>摧毁塔楼</strong>，<strong>跳跃危险区域</strong>，并利用散布在赛道上的<strong>加速装置</strong>抢占优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，<strong>速度不足以获胜</strong>，你必须为胜利而战！</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的多人模式</strong>：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持<strong>2人分屏模式</strong>，挑战你的朋友或家人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持<strong>1个键盘和1个控制器</strong>，为双人比赛提供简单又有趣的体验。</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与AI对战</strong>：与电脑控制的敌人进行动态而充满挑战的战斗，享受无尽的乐趣。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语",
